title: The Gary Null Show
content: What if the Human Papilloma virus does not cause cervical cancer? <!--more--> Norma Erickson is the president of SaneVax, a science based organization that advocates for the safety, effectiveness and affordability of vaccines in order for families and their children to make informed decisions on whether or not to vaccinate.  She is a former writer and business consultant, and her organization is widely regarded as the primary source for information regarding HPV vaccine safety, efficacy and international news.  Her website is SaneVax.org
